WEBVTT

00:00:02.900 --> 00:00:05.967
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:01:27.200 --> 00:01:31.066
HITSUGAYA:
So Aizen wasn't enough for you.

00:01:31.066 --> 00:01:34.734
You couldn't be happy until
you'd hurt Momo as well.

00:01:34.734 --> 00:01:38.266
You slid your lies
into her mind like a dagger

00:01:38.266 --> 00:01:41.166
and twisted them until they were
so painful that her hands bled

00:01:41.166 --> 00:01:43.000
from gripping her sword so hard.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:46.166
I'm sorry.
I'm afraid I don't follow you.

00:01:48.367 --> 00:01:51.900
I gave you a warning.

00:01:51.900 --> 00:01:55.166
I told you
that if you ever hurt Momo,

00:01:55.166 --> 00:01:57.333
I would kill you myself!

00:02:03.033 --> 00:02:05.300
ICHIMARU:
Hmph. This will never do.

00:02:07.734 --> 00:02:11.867
If you insist on drawing your
sword in a place like this,

00:02:11.867 --> 00:02:15.433
then afraid you leave me no
other choice than to stop you.

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:32.100
But Captain Ichimaru--

00:02:32.100 --> 00:02:34.300
Better move back, Izuru,

00:02:34.300 --> 00:02:37.266
unless you feel like dying.

00:02:37.266 --> 00:02:39.166
[GASPS]

00:02:39.166 --> 00:02:40.867
HITSUGAYA:
Don't be stupid, Izuru.

00:02:40.867 --> 00:02:43.600
Just moving back
isn't going to be enough.

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:45.567
In a few minutes,
I promise you,

00:02:45.567 --> 00:02:46.734
you're not going to want to be

00:02:46.734 --> 00:02:49.033
within 10 square miles
of this place.

00:02:49.033 --> 00:02:51.867
So start running
and don't look back.

00:02:51.867 --> 00:02:55.934
Because if you stay here, you're
liable to get drawn into this.

00:02:57.333 --> 00:03:01.500
And I can't guarantee
I won't kill you by mistake.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.500
[GRUNTING]

00:03:05.500 --> 00:03:07.834
[♪♪♪]

00:03:16.934 --> 00:03:18.567
[YELLING]

00:03:28.266 --> 00:03:30.200
ICHIMARU:
An opening.

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:41.667
Evidently, the rumors about
Squad 10's

00:03:41.667 --> 00:03:43.600
Captain Hitsugaya are true.

00:03:43.600 --> 00:03:45.133
A child prodigy of the sword

00:03:45.133 --> 00:03:48.033
that comes along only
once every few centuries.

00:03:48.033 --> 00:03:50.467
How very dangerous you are.

00:03:58.200 --> 00:04:00.300
You're really serious.

00:04:03.500 --> 00:04:05.633
[GROWLS]

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:10.734
IZURU:
Incredible.

00:04:10.734 --> 00:04:14.233
The level of his spiritual
pressure is crushing.

00:04:15.767 --> 00:04:17.800
Now, die!
Hm.

00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:19.266
[SHOUTS]

00:04:30.734 --> 00:04:33.500
[GRUNTING]

00:04:46.400 --> 00:04:49.467
Well, Squad Captain,
what do you think now?

00:04:51.433 --> 00:04:53.900
Do you still like your chances?

00:05:02.266 --> 00:05:05.500
I see.

00:05:05.500 --> 00:05:08.266
I had better not
underestimate you,

00:05:08.266 --> 00:05:10.700
Toshiro Hitsugaya,

00:05:10.700 --> 00:05:15.667
or else I may wind up
regretting it afterwards.

00:05:15.667 --> 00:05:19.066
No, you're wrong about that.

00:05:19.066 --> 00:05:24.533
Because you're going to start
regretting this day right now.

00:05:24.533 --> 00:05:29.333
Remember, it's you who
forced me to do this, Gin.

00:05:29.333 --> 00:05:32.567
And now you're going to pay
for what you did to Momo!

00:05:32.567 --> 00:05:34.567
[GASPS]

00:05:43.500 --> 00:05:44.800
[GRUNTS]

00:05:51.367 --> 00:05:54.667
Rain over the frosted,
frozen sky!

00:06:01.633 --> 00:06:03.900
Hyorinmaru!

00:06:08.834 --> 00:06:12.834
IZURU:
So this is Hyorinmaru,
a dragon of water and ice

00:06:12.834 --> 00:06:15.533
created by overflowing
spiritual pressure.

00:06:15.533 --> 00:06:19.467
In fact, they say it can
even affect the weather.

00:06:19.467 --> 00:06:23.600
I've never seen it before, but
there's no mistaking what it is,

00:06:23.600 --> 00:06:27.233
the released form of Captain
Hitsugaya's Zanpakuto,

00:06:27.233 --> 00:06:29.900
Hyorinmaru.

00:06:29.900 --> 00:06:31.967
[SHOUTS THEN GRUNTS]

00:06:39.867 --> 00:06:42.500
IZURU:
So much water! Such velocity.

00:06:42.500 --> 00:06:44.100
I couldn't dodge it!

00:06:44.100 --> 00:06:45.867
[GASPS]

00:06:45.867 --> 00:06:48.867
[SCREAMS]

00:06:53.700 --> 00:06:56.233
[SHOUTS]

00:07:19.133 --> 00:07:21.100
My captain!

00:07:21.100 --> 00:07:24.066
Now you're done, Gin Ichimaru.

00:07:24.066 --> 00:07:27.934
Pierce his flesh, Shinso.

00:07:33.333 --> 00:07:34.400
Really?

00:07:34.400 --> 00:07:36.500
Are you sure you
want to dodge this?

00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:39.166
If you do, she'll die.

00:07:39.166 --> 00:07:40.533
Momo!

00:07:43.033 --> 00:07:44.266
[GRUNTS]

00:07:47.867 --> 00:07:50.333
Rangiku?

00:07:51.867 --> 00:07:53.867
Please forgive me, sir.

00:07:53.867 --> 00:07:56.433
I was returning to my
quarters as you ordered.

00:07:56.433 --> 00:07:59.767
But then I-- I felt
Hyorinmaru's spiritual pressure

00:07:59.767 --> 00:08:01.233
and thought you might need help.

00:08:01.233 --> 00:08:05.800
Now, Captain Ichimaru,
please put away your sword.

00:08:08.066 --> 00:08:09.567
If you refuse,

00:08:09.567 --> 00:08:13.100
then you're going to have
both of us as your opponents.

00:08:17.300 --> 00:08:18.834
Hm.

00:08:18.834 --> 00:08:20.033
[LAUGHS]

00:08:40.100 --> 00:08:42.333
YORUICHI:
Day is breaking.

00:08:43.900 --> 00:08:47.166
Only two days remaining.

00:08:47.166 --> 00:08:49.734
Ichigo is growing
with startling speed

00:08:49.734 --> 00:08:51.967
compared to ordinary
Soul Reapers.

00:08:51.967 --> 00:08:55.667
The rate of his progress
is hard to believe.

00:08:55.667 --> 00:08:58.333
But only his combat
techniques have improved.

00:08:58.333 --> 00:09:01.967
His spirit energy
has barely changed at all.

00:09:06.300 --> 00:09:08.200
All right.

00:09:08.200 --> 00:09:10.300
Exercise is finished.

00:09:12.233 --> 00:09:15.066
I wonder where Yoruichi
ran off to now.

00:09:15.066 --> 00:09:17.633
It's about time to get started
with the day's training.

00:09:17.633 --> 00:09:19.133
YORUICHI:
At the rate we're going,

00:09:19.133 --> 00:09:21.033
I don't know if he's
going to make it.

00:09:21.033 --> 00:09:24.333
Can he achieve the Bankai
release in only two more days?

00:09:24.333 --> 00:09:27.200
Or should I extend
his training?

00:09:29.300 --> 00:09:31.000
According to the information

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:32.900
I gathered
after we entered the city,

00:09:32.900 --> 00:09:35.800
the grace period
between Rukia's execution date

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:38.333
was supposed to be 25 days.

00:09:38.333 --> 00:09:41.000
We've used up 21
of them already.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.200
That would mean that after

00:09:42.200 --> 00:09:43.967
Ichigo's three days
of training here,

00:09:43.967 --> 00:09:46.333
the execution would be
the following day,

00:09:46.333 --> 00:09:48.100
with no time to spare.

00:09:49.867 --> 00:09:52.467
It turned out we were
chased by that Cleaner

00:09:52.467 --> 00:09:54.233
inside of the Senkaimon,

00:09:54.233 --> 00:09:56.700
and the time frame shifted
in our favor

00:09:56.700 --> 00:09:59.333
when we entered
the Soul Society.

00:10:01.467 --> 00:10:04.734
In other words, even after
our three days of training,

00:10:04.734 --> 00:10:08.433
we still have eight days left
before Rukia's execution.

00:10:08.433 --> 00:10:11.800
So there's definitely time
to extend the training.

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:15.200
But the question is, should I?

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:18.734
This three-day program
was created by Kisuke

00:10:18.734 --> 00:10:21.400
and tested using his own body.

00:10:21.400 --> 00:10:24.767
In fact, he's the only one
who has ever succeeded.

00:10:24.767 --> 00:10:27.600
No one else has ever made
it to Bankai this way.

00:10:27.600 --> 00:10:29.233
Hey, Yoruichi!

00:10:29.233 --> 00:10:31.633
YORUICHI:
In the process,
Kisuke determined

00:10:31.633 --> 00:10:34.266
that three days was both
the minimum and the maximum

00:10:34.266 --> 00:10:37.300
amount of time
needed to acquire the release,

00:10:37.300 --> 00:10:39.200
and that it would be
dangerous to continue

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.133
any longer than that.

00:10:41.133 --> 00:10:43.333
Yoruichi, where are you?

00:10:43.333 --> 00:10:45.200
YORUICHI:
I remember him saying--

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:49.300
Don't worry. Ichigo's abilities
are far superior to my own.

00:10:49.300 --> 00:10:50.567
YORUICHI:
I believed him.

00:10:50.567 --> 00:10:53.300
And here we are,
fully engaged in training.

00:10:53.300 --> 00:10:55.233
Hey, Yoruichi!

00:10:55.233 --> 00:10:56.867
YORUICHI:
But there's no guarantee

00:10:56.867 --> 00:10:59.433
that Ichigo's soul
will be able to withstand

00:10:59.433 --> 00:11:01.300
an extended training period.

00:11:01.300 --> 00:11:04.433
ICHIGO:
Yoruichi, damn it!
Come on out here.

00:11:04.433 --> 00:11:07.266
What are you, afraid of me
all of a sudden and ran away?

00:11:07.266 --> 00:11:09.734
Quit playing games with me
and let's get started!

00:11:09.734 --> 00:11:11.100
You hear me?

00:11:11.100 --> 00:11:13.533
YORUICHI:
I'll give him an extra day.

00:11:13.533 --> 00:11:15.166
And after that,

00:11:15.166 --> 00:11:18.633
if there's still no change
in his spirit energy,

00:11:18.633 --> 00:11:21.300
then we'll just have to
risk it.

00:11:29.433 --> 00:11:31.700
What did you say?

00:11:40.800 --> 00:11:42.834
[GASPS]

00:11:44.667 --> 00:11:47.266
MAN:
Did you not hear
the first time?

00:11:47.266 --> 00:11:50.166
Very well. I shall repeat
the pronouncement.

00:11:50.166 --> 00:11:53.133
By executive order,
your execution date

00:11:53.133 --> 00:11:55.233
has been changed once again.

00:11:55.233 --> 00:11:56.633
Rukia Kuchiki,

00:11:56.633 --> 00:12:01.367
your execution
will be carried out tomorrow.

00:12:16.600 --> 00:12:19.233
If you hadn't shown up
there right when you did,

00:12:19.233 --> 00:12:21.467
Momo would surely be dead now.

00:12:21.467 --> 00:12:24.233
Thank you, Rangiku.

00:12:24.233 --> 00:12:26.367
You're welcome.

00:12:28.667 --> 00:12:30.667
[♪♪♪]

00:12:30.667 --> 00:12:32.200
[GRUNTS]

00:12:40.066 --> 00:12:42.734
[PANTING]

00:12:48.333 --> 00:12:49.667
Hm.

00:12:49.667 --> 00:12:51.467
I'm not done with you yet!

00:12:51.467 --> 00:12:54.667
Instead of coming after me,

00:12:54.667 --> 00:12:57.934
maybe you should look after
the Squad Five lieutenant.

00:13:08.100 --> 00:13:10.967
RANGIKU:
Once again, you disappear

00:13:10.967 --> 00:13:14.166
without telling
me where you're going.

00:13:14.166 --> 00:13:18.333
That's one thing about
you that's never changed.

00:13:19.767 --> 00:13:22.400
Gin, tell me,

00:13:22.400 --> 00:13:25.233
where are you going now?

00:13:34.033 --> 00:13:36.633
HITSUGAYA:
That letter
of Captain Aizen's...

00:13:36.633 --> 00:13:40.734
I wish I knew how much
of it was forged.

00:13:42.133 --> 00:13:46.300
[SCREAMING]
Captain Aizen!

00:13:46.300 --> 00:13:48.834
[CRIES]

00:13:51.133 --> 00:13:54.333
HITSUGAYA:
The part in there about using
the power of Sokyoku

00:13:54.333 --> 00:13:57.300
released by Rukia Kuchiki's
execution...

00:13:57.300 --> 00:13:59.367
is that real?

00:13:59.367 --> 00:14:01.834
Is there really a plot
to use that power

00:14:01.834 --> 00:14:04.633
to destroy all of
the Soul Society?

00:14:04.633 --> 00:14:07.367
Could that line have been true?

00:14:11.834 --> 00:14:16.800
If it is true,
if that's Ichimaru's aim,

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:20.934
then I know what I have to do.

00:14:20.934 --> 00:14:22.867
A hell butterfly?

00:14:22.867 --> 00:14:25.533
The following is
an urgent message

00:14:25.533 --> 00:14:27.834
for all squad captains
and their lieutenants.

00:14:27.834 --> 00:14:30.233
A change has been made

00:14:30.233 --> 00:14:32.767
regarding the execution
of Rukia Kuchiki.

00:14:32.767 --> 00:14:35.767
Be advised that this convicted
prisoner's execution

00:14:35.767 --> 00:14:39.700
is now set
for 29 hours from now.

00:14:39.700 --> 00:14:42.100
This decision is final
and irrevocable.

00:14:42.100 --> 00:14:45.333
There will be no further
changes to the execution date.

00:14:45.333 --> 00:14:47.767
That is all.

00:14:49.133 --> 00:14:51.033
[GRUNTS]

00:14:51.033 --> 00:14:52.867
Captain?

00:14:52.867 --> 00:14:57.800
The execution and the release
of Sokyoku's power...

00:14:57.800 --> 00:15:00.233
If Gin really is
the one behind this,

00:15:00.233 --> 00:15:02.500
then there's no way
I can just stand by

00:15:02.500 --> 00:15:04.233
and let his plan go forward.

00:15:04.233 --> 00:15:05.700
Let's go, Rangiku.

00:15:05.700 --> 00:15:07.333
You know what we have to do.

00:15:07.333 --> 00:15:10.700
Stop the execution.

00:15:10.700 --> 00:15:12.333
[♪♪♪]

00:15:12.333 --> 00:15:14.934
MAN [OVER PA]:
The following is an urgent
message for all

00:15:14.934 --> 00:15:17.934
court guard squad captains
and their lieutenants.

00:15:17.934 --> 00:15:19.700
Another change has been made

00:15:19.700 --> 00:15:23.400
regarding the execution date
of Rukia Kuchiki.

00:15:23.400 --> 00:15:26.000
Be advised that
the prisoner's execution

00:15:26.000 --> 00:15:29.433
is now set for 29 hours
from now.

00:15:29.433 --> 00:15:33.734
I repeat, the execution
of Rukia Kuchiki

00:15:33.734 --> 00:15:37.633
is set for 29 hours from now.

00:15:37.633 --> 00:15:41.233
This decision is final
and irrevocable.

00:15:41.233 --> 00:15:44.533
There will be no further
changes to the execution date.

00:15:44.533 --> 00:15:46.300
That is all.

00:16:11.500 --> 00:16:13.667
There's no doubt.

00:16:13.667 --> 00:16:16.033
That's his spiritual pressure.

00:16:16.033 --> 00:16:18.100
[GRUNTING]

00:16:37.266 --> 00:16:40.433
YORUICHI:
Ichigo's making
steady progress.

00:16:40.433 --> 00:16:43.700
But still, I just
can't seem to shake

00:16:43.700 --> 00:16:45.400
this uneasy feeling I have.

00:16:45.400 --> 00:16:46.734
[YELLING]

00:16:46.734 --> 00:16:49.266
I'm sensing something
out there,

00:16:49.266 --> 00:16:52.867
something ominous approaching
this place.

00:16:56.834 --> 00:16:57.967
[GASPS]

00:16:57.967 --> 00:17:00.433
RENJI:
I was wondering
what you could be doing,

00:17:00.433 --> 00:17:02.400
holed up in this place.

00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:04.166
I take it
that's the true form

00:17:04.166 --> 00:17:07.100
of your Zanpakuto
there with you.

00:17:10.200 --> 00:17:13.467
So you're hiding out here

00:17:13.467 --> 00:17:16.166
and secretly training
for Bankai, are you?

00:17:16.166 --> 00:17:18.066
Looks like fun to me.

00:17:18.066 --> 00:17:19.500
[GASPS]

00:17:23.400 --> 00:17:25.433
Let me train along with you.

00:17:25.433 --> 00:17:27.400
Renji.

00:17:27.400 --> 00:17:30.633
You seem to have that
"what are you doing here?" look.

00:17:30.633 --> 00:17:33.734
Hell, I guess I can't
blame you for wondering.

00:17:33.734 --> 00:17:37.900
But the fact is, I'm not
here for any special reason.

00:17:37.900 --> 00:17:40.100
It's just that we're
out of time now.

00:17:40.100 --> 00:17:42.600
So I needed some place
where I could concentrate

00:17:42.600 --> 00:17:45.333
and train in peace,
just like you.

00:17:45.333 --> 00:17:48.800
What do you mean
we're out of time?

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:50.867
What the hell are
you talking about?

00:17:55.333 --> 00:17:56.767
Well, all right.

00:17:56.767 --> 00:17:59.233
I guess I can at least
tell you that much.

00:18:00.400 --> 00:18:02.700
It's about Rukia's execution.

00:18:02.700 --> 00:18:04.433
They've changed the time.

00:18:04.433 --> 00:18:07.300
Changed the time?

00:18:07.300 --> 00:18:12.100
They've announced it's going
to be at noon. Noon tomorrow.

00:18:12.100 --> 00:18:13.667
[GRUNTS]

00:18:13.667 --> 00:18:16.066
[GASPS]

00:18:16.066 --> 00:18:18.567
And though I hate to admit it,

00:18:18.567 --> 00:18:20.100
the fact is,
at my current level,

00:18:20.100 --> 00:18:23.000
I'm not quite good enough
to save Rukia.

00:18:23.000 --> 00:18:26.066
That's why I came here.
To train.

00:18:26.066 --> 00:18:28.400
Don't worry about me.

00:18:28.400 --> 00:18:30.600
I don't have any
intention of getting in the way

00:18:30.600 --> 00:18:31.967
of your Bankai training.

00:18:31.967 --> 00:18:35.900
In fact, I'm close to achieving
the Bankai release myself.

00:18:35.900 --> 00:18:39.500
I've already mastered
manifesting it, like this.

00:18:47.100 --> 00:18:48.800
So if it's okay with you,

00:18:48.800 --> 00:18:51.467
I'm just gonna do
my own thing here.

00:18:58.934 --> 00:19:00.433
Noon tomorrow?

00:19:00.433 --> 00:19:01.967
No way.

00:19:01.967 --> 00:19:04.900
There's no way he can
reach Bankai that quickly.

00:19:07.467 --> 00:19:08.633
ICHIGO:
What?

00:19:08.633 --> 00:19:10.900
Are you just going to
give up on me then?

00:19:10.900 --> 00:19:12.300
Come on, Yoruichi.

00:19:12.300 --> 00:19:15.467
You're the one who started
me on this training program.

00:19:15.467 --> 00:19:19.233
It was your idea, so you can't
be the first one to quit on it.

00:19:19.233 --> 00:19:20.667
Ichigo, no.

00:19:20.667 --> 00:19:23.233
What if tomorrow comes and you
still can't achieve Bankai?

00:19:23.233 --> 00:19:25.266
We can't waste time
worrying about what-ifs.

00:19:25.266 --> 00:19:29.734
Failure is no longer an option.

00:19:29.734 --> 00:19:32.333
If they have changed
the deadline to tomorrow...

00:19:34.166 --> 00:19:37.667
then the only option there is
is to finish training today.

00:19:37.667 --> 00:19:39.834
[♪♪♪]

00:19:48.700 --> 00:19:50.400
YORUICHI:
His spiritual pressure.

00:19:54.233 --> 00:19:56.000
Ichigo.

00:20:09.934 --> 00:20:12.500
RUKIA:
So tomorrow I die.

00:20:12.500 --> 00:20:15.800
I wonder if before
the execution,

00:20:15.800 --> 00:20:18.266
it would be worth begging
for Ichigo and the others

00:20:18.266 --> 00:20:20.900
to be allowed to return
to the World of the Living.

00:20:20.900 --> 00:20:23.934
I belong to the Kuchiki clan,
after all.

00:20:23.934 --> 00:20:25.900
They might allow it.

00:20:30.400 --> 00:20:33.567
It seems strange,
but even when I heard

00:20:33.567 --> 00:20:38.400
that my execution was set
for tomorrow, I wasn't sad.

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:42.967
It must be because
of the dream I had last night,

00:20:42.967 --> 00:20:47.700
that dream about
the night I can never forget.

00:20:56.300 --> 00:20:58.633
RUKIA:
Kaien, sir.

00:21:00.066 --> 00:21:02.467
Kaien!

00:21:02.467 --> 00:21:04.300
Kaien!

00:21:04.300 --> 00:21:06.400
Kaien.

00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:10.000
[CRYING]
Don't.

00:21:10.000 --> 00:21:11.367
You can't die on me.

00:21:11.367 --> 00:21:13.433
[SOBBING]

00:21:16.333 --> 00:21:19.333
Kaien, you can't go!

00:21:26.667 --> 00:21:28.600
[♪♪♪]

00:21:28.600 --> 00:21:30.433
♪ Happypeople ♪

00:21:30.433 --> 00:21:33.066
♪ Come on, come on
Come on ♪

00:21:33.066 --> 00:21:35.367
♪ Happypeople ♪

00:21:35.367 --> 00:21:36.767
♪ Here we go ♪

00:21:36.767 --> 00:21:39.934
♪ Everybody stand up ♪

00:21:39.934 --> 00:21:43.400
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:52.967
♪ Keep your head right up ♪

00:21:52.967 --> 00:21:54.266
♪ To the sky ♪

00:21:54.266 --> 00:21:55.500
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:21:55.500 --> 00:21:56.600
♪ Oh, yeah ♪

00:21:56.600 --> 00:21:57.767
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:21:57.767 --> 00:21:59.867
♪ Oh, yeah ♪
♪ Just call me any time ♪

00:21:59.867 --> 00:22:01.033
♪ Oh, yeah ♪

00:22:01.033 --> 00:22:03.200
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:22:03.200 --> 00:22:07.533
♪ Happypeople's in the house ♪

00:22:07.533 --> 00:22:10.867
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:22:11.867 --> 00:22:16.166
♪ Happypeople's in the house ♪

00:22:16.166 --> 00:22:19.400
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

00:22:19.400 --> 00:22:20.600
♪ Well... ♪

00:22:20.600 --> 00:22:23.233
♪ Happypeople ♪
♪ In the house ♪

00:22:24.100 --> 00:22:25.433
♪ All right ♪

00:22:25.433 --> 00:22:26.834
♪ Happypeople ♪

00:22:26.834 --> 00:22:29.533
♪ Mmm, happy ♪

00:22:31.734 --> 00:22:33.734
[RAIN PATTERING]

00:22:36.100 --> 00:22:37.600
RUKIA:
Kaien...

00:22:38.633 --> 00:22:42.767
I'm afraid
there is nothing of me

00:22:42.767 --> 00:22:44.467
that's worth saving.

